"indent":[]},"value":"lang.java.lib.collection.interface.list.vector"}],"anchors":{"vector-is-legacy-class--longer-method-names":{"type":"header","text":"Vector is legacy class ⇒ Longer method names","value":"vector-is-legacy-class--longer-method-names","line":25,"column":0,"depth":2},"child-classesinterfaces":{"type":"header","text":"Child classes/interfaces","value":"child-classesinterfaces","line":43,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["ovqyygo1fe3tpwf200ymr1e"],"parent":"uzes06s5i7rok1c91ok4ici","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"vector\">Vector<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#vector\"></a></h1>\n<p>implements <a href=\"/cs/notes/uzes06s5i7rok1c91ok4ici\">List</a> and <a href=\"/cs/notes/ovg9du1v373av7mahmf6xd3\">RandomAccess</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Underlying Data Structure: Resizable <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">data.structure.primary.array (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/esvk57cujir0xgnugroobcg\">Duplicates - Allowed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/c8sos8r4mdfod3yi0hrbxxs\">Insertion Order - Preserved</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/ub2twkupmr0kns22xaxz8tj\">null insetion - Allowed</a></li>\n<li>Best choice for: Frequent retrievel</li>\n<li>Worst choice for: Frequent insertion/deletion in middle</li>\n<li>Constructors:\n<ol>\n<li><code>Vector v = new Vector();</code></li>\n<li><code>Vector v = new Vector(int initialCapacity);</code></li>\n<li><code>Vector v = new Vector(int initialCapacity, int incrementalCapacity);</code></li>\n<li><code>Vector v = new Vector(Collection C);</code></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>Default initial capacity: 10</li>\n<li>Load factor/fill ratio:</li>\n<li>New Capacity: 2C</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"vector-is-legacy-class--longer-method-names\">Vector is legacy class ⇒ Longer method names<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#vector-is-legacy-class--longer-method-names\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Adding </p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/rpb0p7ld8g30mdscf1r32re\">Collection Interface</a> - <code>add(Object O)</code></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/uzes06s5i7rok1c91ok4ici\">List</a> - <code>add(int index, Object O)</code></li>\n<li>In vector, <code>addElement(Object O)</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Removing</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/rpb0p7ld8g30mdscf1r32re\">Collection Interface</a> - <code>remove(Object O)</code></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/uzes06s5i7rok1c91ok4ici\">List</a> \n<ul>\n<li><code>remove(int index)</code></li>\n<li><code>clear()</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>In vector,\n<ul>\n<li><code>removeElement(Object O)</code></li>\n<li><code>removeElementAt(int index)</code></li>\n<li><code>removeAllElements()</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"child-classesinterfaces\">Child classes/interfaces<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#child-classesinterfaces\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/cs/notes/ovqyygo1fe3tpwf200ymr1e\">Stack</a></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/ovqyygo1fe3tpwf200ymr1e\">Stack</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/fi3xznhjsf8ezkolih7torp\">Collection Frameworks Cheatsheet (cs)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/uzes06s5i7rok1c91ok4ici\">List (cs)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/4x38t5zqngoe33sug8ec87p\">Enumeration (cs)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/ovqyygo1fe3tpwf200ymr1e\">Stack (cs)</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"7ncn3al6mmutkhgoesulce9","title":"Computer Science","desc":"","updated":1715103618849,"created":1713296516553,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"cs"},"contentHash":"36faf26c6be438d4aed355d72b55a110","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"7ncn3al6mmutkhgoesulce9","vaultName":"cs"},"value":"arch","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":3,"offset":105},"end":{"line":6,"column